code: protected void setupHttpConduit(HTTPConduit httpConduit) {     TLSClientParameters tlsClientParameters = tryToGetTLSClientParametersFromConduit(httpConduit).     tlsClientParameters.setSSLSocketFactory(tryToGetSSLSocketFactory()).     httpConduit.setTlsClientParameters(tlsClientParameters). }
